                <div class=3D"page-header">
                    <h1><b>8-bit Checksum Calculator</b></h1>
                </div>
                <div>
                   =20
                    <div class=3D"well">
                        <p>
                            This 8-bit Checksum Calculator can be used to c=
alculate the 8-bit Checksum of a sequence of hexadecimal values or bytes.
                            The bytes and be entered in a string of two cha=
racter. The character can be entered in either upper case or lower case.
                            8-bit Checksum is also called the 2's complimen=
t of addition of all bytes.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Enter Hexadecimal value separated by space e.g.=
 if you have "0xaa 0xaa 0xaa" then enter "aa aa aa" and press
                            the "calculate" button to calculate the 8-bit c=
hecksum.
                            the checksum of string of all entered bytes and=
 the checksum will be equal to zero.
                            e,g.
                            <br>
                            The checksum Entered byte string   "aa aa" =3D =
"ac"
                            <br>
                            The checksum of  "aa aa ac" =3D "0"
                        </p>
                        <form role=3D"form">
                            <div class=3D"form-group">
                                <label for=3D"N:">Enter Hexadecimal (Hex):<=
/label>
                                <input type=3D"text" class=3D"form-control"=
 size=3D"128" name=3D"N">
                            </div>
                            <br>
                            <button class=3D"btn  btn-lg btn-success" type=
=3D"button" name=3D"calc" value=3D"Calculate">
                                Calculate
                            </button>
